        direction TB

        Sally["Sally SCADA Platform<br/><br/><i>Smart Grid Monitoring &<br/>Control System</i><br/><br/>• Real-time grid visualization<br/>• Rule-based anomaly detection<br/>• Setpoint management<br/>• Co-simulation support"]
    end

    %% External Actors
    Operator["👤 Grid Operator<br/><br/><i>Monitors grid state,<br/>configures rules,<br/>applies setpoints</i>"]

    Engineer["👤 Control Engineer<br/><br/><i>Configures simulations,<br/>analyzes performance,<br/>reviews telemetry</i>"]

